
THESE TRACKS CAN ONLY BE PLAYED IF YOU OWN THE FULL GAME
--------------------------------------------------------

Floppy Users
------------

1 - Format a blank floppy disk.

2 - Ensure the disk is named XTR6.

3 - Copy all the files in the XTR6 dir onto the XTR6 floppy disk.

4 - From the game select play single track, and insert this disk into the
    drive.



HD Users
--------

Copy the following directories to the directory in which XTR was installed :

Backgrounds
Layouts
Tiles
Tracks
Worlds

When the game is next booted, select play single track and you will find
the new tracks are available.

